@Sony has been my greatest ally in sharing our ocean’s story and bringing the solutions that can protect its future to a global audience. They have provided me and my team @SeaLegacy the tools to test the limits of photography and shatter the barriers between people and the last of our planet’s wild places. @SonyAlpha cameras have been my trusted companions beneath the waves for the last 13 years and I am thrilled to help support the launch of the new Sony Alpha 1; the camera that will revolutionize the way we see and document the world. Head over to @SonyAlpha and join me in welcoming this game-changer to the field of photography and the visual arts. With it, we will bring vast audiences closer than ever before to the beauty of our natural world and shine a light on the innovative solutions to our planet’s greatest challenges.
@keshalambert @paulnicklen @jnsilva @charlysavely @phil.yoon @edsel 
Directed by @curtismorgan #BeAlpha

#Ad / Collaborations take many shapes and my absolute favorites are those in which story and purpose align to form partnerships with true impact. That is when I know I am in the right place with the right people. Go Beyond, with @northsails_collection is one of those partnerships. This month, they are shining a light on my dear friends, @coralGardeners from French Polynesia. When I first met @Toutiess (Titouan), now a fellow North Sails Ocean Hero, I had the privilege of capturing these images of his team hard at work beneath the waves to restore the reefs of their home in Moorea. These fragile, yet invaluable ecosystems have the power to stand against growing storms and replenish our seas with new life, building resilience across the entire ocean. Thanks to Titouan and the Coral Gardeners crew, our ocean’s abundance may thrive once more and give our planet the chance it needs to recover. 
@northsails_collection has a limited-edition capsule dedicated to the Coral Gardeners. Click the link in my bio to learn more.

